  "title": "WAREHOUSE ASSISTANTS [FULL TIME| MON-FRI 1PM-11PM | WEST | SIGN ON BONUS | FAST HIRING]",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Pet Lovers Centre:</strong></p><p>Pet Lovers Centre Pte Ltd is one of the largest and oldest pet care retail chain in Southeast Asia since founded in 1973. Pet Lovers Centre Group, which currently leads 6 subsidiaries, is headquarted in Singapore and currently has over 150 outlets spanning across 5 countries in South-East Asia.</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Highlights:</strong></u></p><ul><li>🗓️ 5 days work week (Monday - Friday. 1.00pm-11.00pm)</li><li>📍 Work Location: 7 Toh Tuck Link, Singapore 596227</li><li>💰$4 meal allowance on fulfilled workdays only</li><li>💰 Sign-on Bonus: $200 on completion of every 2 months of continuous service during the first 6 months of service</li><li>📈 Productivity Target Incentives up to $320</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Support the day-to-day warehouse operations</li><li>Assist and perform loading and unloading of containers</li><li>Perform goods receiving function and ensure accuracy in goods received</li><li>Perform picking and packing function based on the DO requirement for delivery to the retail outlets / customers</li><li>Ensure that the inventory system is updated accurately and promptly</li><li>Perform general housekeeping of the warehouse</li><li>Adhere to the SOP as set for warehouse operations</li><li>Any other duties / tasks as assigned</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>No experience needed</li><li>Must be able to commit to the working hours as stated</li><li>Prior warehouse experience is advantageous</li><li>Comfortable to work in non-air con & warehouse environment</li><li>Able to carry products weighing up to 20kg</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Benefits:</strong></u></p><ul><li>✅ Attendance and picking accuracy money incentives</li><li>✅ Medical Reimbursement, Health Insurance</li><li>✅ Staff Purchase Discount</li><li>✅ Career Development</li><li>✅ Long Service Award</li><li>✅ Company Uniform Provided</li><li>✅ Air-conditioned staff lounge</li></ul><p>⭐ If you are interested, please apply via our career website: https://plc.applyourjobs.com.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
